{"type":"message","id":"192f0e45","parentId":"4da74a7f","timestamp":"2026-02-27T05:27:47.561Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"functions.read:51","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\n  \"mcpServers\": {\n    \"ddgs_search\": {\n      \"command\": \"python\",\n      \"args\": [\"D:\\\\gooddog\\\\scripts\\\\mcp_ddgs_server.py\"]\n    },\n    \"dashscope_websearch\": {\n      \"url\": \"https://dashscope.aliyuncs.com/api/v1/mcps/WebSearch/mcp\",\n      \"headers\": {\"Authorization\": \"Bearer sk-8937a309c5f04f909aabd1ad255b3654\"}\n    },\n    \"image-recognition\": {\n      \"command\": \"npx\",\n      \"args\": [\"-y\", \"@mcpcn/image-recognition-mcp\"],\n      \"env\": {\"DASHSCOPE_API_KEY\": \"sk-8937a309c5f04f909aabd1ad255b3654\"}\n    },\n    \"paddleocr-mcp\": {\n      \"command\": \"python\",\n      \"args\": [\"D:\\\\.openclaw\\\\.openclaw\\\\workspace\\\\mcp-servers\\\\paddleocr-mcp\\\\server.py\"]\n    },\n    \"playwright\": {\n      \"command\": \"npx\",\n      \"args\": [\"-y\", \"@microsoft/playwright-mcp\"]\n    },\n    \"filesystem\": {\n      \"command\": \"npx\",\n      \"args\": [\"-y\", \"@modelcontextprotocol/server-filesystem\", \"D:\\\\.openclaw\"]\n    },\n    \"mcp-grep\": {\n      \"command\": \"npx\",\n      \"args\": [\"-y\", \"@247arjun/mcp-grep\"]\n    }\n  },\n  \"imports\": []\n}\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1772170067556}}
{"type":"message","id":"c7a2820c","parentId":"192f0e45","timestamp":"2026-02-27T05:28:03.314Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"看到了！cursor大哥给我加了两个新MCP：\n\n## 1. filesystem - 官方文件系统MCP\n```json\n\"filesystem\": {\n  \"command\": \"npx\",\n  \"args\": [\"-y\", \"@modelcontextprotocol/server-filesystem\", \"D:\\\\.openclaw\"]\n}\n```\n**作用**：强力文件操作，可以访问 `D:\\.openclaw` 目录树（安全限制）。\n**工具**：`read_file`, `write_file`, `edit_file`, `list_directory`, `search_files`, `grep_files`, `create_directory`, `move_file`, `get_file_info`\n\n## 2. mcp-grep - 专用内容搜索MCP\n```json\n\"mcp-grep\": {\n  \"command\": \"npx\",\n  \"args\": [\"-y\", \"@247arjun/mcp-grep\"]\n}\n```\n**作用**：在项目里做强力内容搜索，支持自然语言描述搜索意图。\n**工具**：`grep_search_intent`, `grep_regex`, `grep_count`, `grep_files_with_matches`, `grep_advanced`\n\n这俩都是好货啊！filesystem比我自己自带的read/write更强，mcp-grep能在项目里做代码搜索。\n\n要我现在试试用用看？比如用mcp-grep搜一下项目里的某个关键词？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"bailian","model":"kimi-k2.5","usage":{"input":57832,"output":272,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":58104,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1772170067562}}
