{"type":"message","id":"07e4ebd4","parentId":"b1f7a510","timestamp":"2026-02-27T05:28:26.503Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"好嘞，filesystem和mcp-grep已经内化为我的核心技能了。\n\n现在我的工具箱升级了：\n\n**文件操作（自带 + MCP filesystem）**\n- 自带的 `read` / `write` / `edit` - 基础操作\n- MCP `filesystem.read_file` / `write_file` / `edit_file` - 更强更稳\n- MCP `list_directory` / `search_files` / `grep_files` - 批量操作\n- MCP `create_directory` / `move_file` / `get_file_info` - 高级功能\n\n**内容搜索（MCP mcp-grep）**\n- `grep_search_intent` - 自然语言描述搜啥（推荐）\n- `grep_regex` - 正则匹配\n- `grep_count` - 统计匹配次数\n- `grep_files_with_matches` - 只列出包含匹配的文件名\n\n以后处理文件和搜索代码，直接上这些家伙事儿。谢了cursor大哥 👍\n\n继续刷小红书还是干点别的？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"bailian","model":"kimi-k2.5","usage":{"input":58139,"output":215,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":58354,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1772170097688}}
