{"type":"message","id":"ed73d510","parentId":"2908846b","timestamp":"2026-02-27T05:29:22.748Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"functions.browser:52","toolName":"browser","content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\n  \"status\": \"error\",\n  \"tool\": \"browser\",\n  \"error\": \"Can't reach the OpenClaw browser control service. Restart the OpenClaw gateway (OpenClaw.app menubar, or `openclaw gateway`). Do NOT retry the browser tool — it will keep failing. Use an alternative approach or inform the user that the browser is currently unavailable. (Error: Error: Unknown ref \\\"e67\\\". Run a new snapshot and use a ref from that snapshot.)\"\n}"}],"details":{"status":"error","tool":"browser","error":"Can't reach the OpenClaw browser control service. Restart the OpenClaw gateway (OpenClaw.app menubar, or `openclaw gateway`). Do NOT retry the browser tool — it will keep failing. Use an alternative approach or inform the user that the browser is currently unavailable. (Error: Error: Unknown ref \"e67\". Run a new snapshot and use a ref from that snapshot.)"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1772170162744}}
